Sinew ignored the primitive robot's comments, raising a fist and a large 
burst of electricity firing off at Grimlock.  "Prepare for extermination by 
the authority of the IGL."

The skimmer Cliffjumper was pounding on continued on its descent towards a 
landing bay, a few dozen figures on the ground awaiting its landing.
